items.content:
Laravel Boost MCP:<ul><li data-empty="false">In your Laravel project terminal: composer require laravel/boost --dev</li><li data-empty="false">In Antigravity's MCP Config:JSON"laravel-boost": {
  "command": "php",
  "args": ["artisan", "boost:mcp"]
}
</li><li data-empty="false">Benefit: Provides the agent with instant access to Laravel routes, migrations, models, and Artisan commands without scanning files.</li></ul>

Next.js DevTools MCP:<ul><li data-empty="false">Ensure your Next.js dev server is running: npm run dev in your frontend project's terminal.</li><li data-empty="false">In Antigravity's MCP Config:JSON"next-devtools": {
  "command": "npx",
  "args": ["-y", "next-devtools-mcp@latest"]
}
</li><li data-empty="false">Benefit: Gives the agent real-time insights into your running Next.js application, including component states, route structures, and build errors.</li></ul>

